<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Tu presupuesto Citribio está listo — Pedido #{{ order.id }}</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f5f3ee;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#1a2e1c;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%;-ms-text-size-adjust:100%;">

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="background-color:#f5f3ee;">
  <tr>
    <td align="center" style="padding:36px 12px;">

      <!-- ── Email card ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"
             style="max-width:660px;margin:0 auto;background-color:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.09);">

        <!-- ── Header ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
        <tr>
          <td align="center" style="background-color:#567f0b;padding:32px 36px 28px;">
            {% if logoUrl is defined and logoUrl %}
              <img src="{{ logoUrl }}" alt="Citribio" width="160"
                   style="display:block;margin:0 auto 20px;height:64px;width:auto;max-width:200px;" />
            {% else %}
              <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin-bottom:14px;">CITRIBIO</div>
            {% endif %}
            <h1 style="margin:0 0 10px;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;line-height:1.2;">
              Tu pedido de Citribio ha sido revisado
            </h1>
            <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.88);line-height:1.55;">
              Pedido <strong style="color:#ffffff;">#{{ order.id }}</strong>
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- ── Greeting ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:28px 36px 0;">
            <p style="margin:0 0 10px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#1a2e1c;">
              Hola {{ ((customer.name ?? '') ~ ' ' ~ (customer.lastName ?? ''))|trim ?: 'cliente' }},
            </p>
            <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#4a5e4c;line-height:1.7;">
              Hemos revisado tu solicitud de pedido y ya tienes disponible el presupuesto final. Para confirmar el pedido, realiza la transferencia bancaria usando los datos indicados a continuación.
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- ── Order + Customer data ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:24px 36px 0;">
            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
              <tr>

                <!-- Order data -->
                <td width="46%" valign="top" style="padding-right:10px;">
                  <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;color:#7a7060;margin-bottom:10px;">Datos del pedido</div>
                  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"
                         style="background-color:#f8f6f2;border:1px solid #e6e0d4;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:11px 16px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;white-space:nowrap;">Nº Pedido</td>
                      <td style="padding:11px 16px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a2e1c;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;">#{{ order.id }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:11px 16px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;white-space:nowrap;">Fecha</td>
                      <td style="padding:11px 16px;font-size:13px;color:#1a2e1c;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;">{{ order.createdAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:11px 16px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;white-space:nowrap;">Estado</td>
                      <td style="padding:11px 16px;">
                        <span style="display:inline-block;background-color:#eef4e3;color:#3d5a08;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;border:1px solid #c8e6a0;">
                          Presupuesto enviado
                        </span>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </td>

                <!-- Customer data -->
                <td width="54%" valign="top" style="padding-left:10px;">
                  <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;color:#7a7060;margin-bottom:10px;">Tus datos</div>
                  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"
                         style="background-color:#f8f6f2;border:1px solid #e6e0d4;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:11px 16px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;white-space:nowrap;">Nombre</td>
                      <td style="padding:11px 16px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a2e1c;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;">{{ ((customer.name ?? '') ~ ' ' ~ (customer.lastName ?? ''))|trim ?: 'N/D' }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:11px 16px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;white-space:nowrap;">Email</td>
                      <td style="padding:11px 16px;font-size:13px;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;word-break:break-all;">{{ customer.email ?: 'N/D' }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:11px 16px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;white-space:nowrap;">Teléfono</td>
                      <td style="padding:11px 16px;font-size:13px;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;">{{ customer.phone ?: 'N/D' }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:11px 16px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;white-space:nowrap;vertical-align:top;">Dirección</td>
                      <td style="padding:11px 16px;font-size:13px;color:#1a2e1c;line-height:1.5;">{{ order.deliveryAddressSnapshot ?: 'N/D' }}</td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </td>

              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- ── Products table ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:28px 36px 0;">
            <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.8px;color:#1a2e1c;margin-bottom:14px;">
              Detalle del presupuesto
            </div>
            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"
                   style="border-collapse:collapse;border:1px solid #e6e0d4;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;">
              <thead>
                <tr style="background-color:#eef4e3;">
                  <th align="left"   style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#3d5a08;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;border-bottom:1px solid #dde8cc;">Producto</th>
                  <th align="left"   style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#3d5a08;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;border-bottom:1px solid #dde8cc;">Variedad / Formato</th>
                  <th align="center" style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#3d5a08;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;border-bottom:1px solid #dde8cc;">Cant.</th>
                  <th align="right"  style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#3d5a08;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;border-bottom:1px solid #dde8cc;">P. Unit.</th>
                  <th align="right"  style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#3d5a08;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;border-bottom:1px solid #dde8cc;">Subtotal</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
              {% for item in items %}
                {% set rowBg = loop.index is odd ? '#ffffff' : '#faf8f4' %}
                <tr style="background-color:{{ rowBg }};">
                  <td style="padding:12px 14px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#1a2e1c;border-bottom:1px solid #ede8df;">{{ item.product }}</td>
                  <td style="padding:12px 14px;font-size:12px;color:#4a5e4c;border-bottom:1px solid #ede8df;line-height:1.6;">
                    {%- set hasDetails = false -%}
                    {% if item.caliber is defined and item.caliber and item.caliber != '-' %}
                      <span style="display:block;">Cal: {{ item.caliber }}</span>
                      {%- set hasDetails = true -%}
                    {% endif %}
                    {% if item.quality is defined and item.quality and item.quality != '-' %}
                      <span style="display:block;">{{ item.quality }}</span>
                      {%- set hasDetails = true -%}
                    {% endif %}
                    {% if item.format is defined and item.format and item.format != '-' %}
                      <span style="display:block;">{{ item.format }}</span>
                      {%- set hasDetails = true -%}
                    {% endif %}
                    {% if not hasDetails %}—{% endif %}
                  </td>
                  <td align="center" style="padding:12px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #ede8df;">
                    <span style="display:inline-block;background-color:#567f0b;color:#ffffff;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 11px;border-radius:20px;min-width:28px;text-align:center;">
                      {{ item.quantity }}
                    </span>
                  </td>
                  <td align="right" style="padding:12px 14px;font-size:13px;color:#1a2e1c;border-bottom:1px solid #ede8df;white-space:nowrap;">
                    {{ item.unitPrice|number_format(2, ',', '.') }} €
                  </td>
                  <td align="right" style="padding:12px 14px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a2e1c;border-bottom:1px solid #ede8df;white-space:nowrap;">
                    {{ item.lineTotal|number_format(2, ',', '.') }} €
                  </td>
                </tr>
              {% endfor %}
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- ── Totals summary ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:20px 36px 0;">
            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
              <tr>
                <td align="right">
                  <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="min-width:280px;">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:7px 0;font-size:13px;color:#7a7060;">Subtotal productos</td>
                      <td align="right" style="padding:7px 0 7px 28px;font-size:13px;color:#1a2e1c;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap;">
                        {{ productsSubtotal|number_format(2, ',', '.') }} €
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:7px 0;font-size:13px;color:#7a7060;">Gastos de envío</td>
                      <td align="right" style="padding:7px 0 7px 28px;font-size:13px;color:#1a2e1c;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap;">
                        {{ shippingPrice|number_format(2, ',', '.') }} €
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td colspan="2" style="padding:6px 0;">
                        <div style="border-top:2px solid #80ba1b;"></div>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:8px 0 0;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#1a2e1c;">TOTAL</td>
                      <td align="right" style="padding:8px 0 0 28px;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#80ba1b;white-space:nowrap;">
                        {{ totalPrice|number_format(2, ',', '.') }} €
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- ── Bank transfer block ────────────────────────────────────────── -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:28px 36px 0;">
            <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.8px;color:#1a2e1c;margin-bottom:14px;">
              Datos para realizar la transferencia
            </div>
            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"
                   style="background-color:#f8f6f2;border:1px solid #e6e0d4;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;">
              <tr>
                <td style="padding:13px 18px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;white-space:nowrap;width:36%;">Titular</td>
                <td style="padding:13px 18px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a2e1c;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;">Citribio</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="padding:13px 18px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;white-space:nowrap;">IBAN</td>
                <td style="padding:13px 18px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a2e1c;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;letter-spacing:0.5px;">{{ bankIban }}</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="padding:13px 18px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;white-space:nowrap;">Importe</td>
                <td style="padding:13px 18px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#80ba1b;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;">{{ totalPrice|number_format(2, ',', '.') }} €</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="padding:13px 18px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;white-space:nowrap;vertical-align:top;">Concepto</td>
                <td style="padding:13px 18px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#ff731d;letter-spacing:0.2px;">{{ transferReference }}</td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- ── Transfer concept warning ───────────────────────────────────── -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:16px 36px 0;">
            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
              <tr>
                <td style="background-color:#fff8f0;border-left:4px solid #ff731d;border-radius:0 10px 10px 0;padding:14px 18px;">
                  <p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#7a3a0a;line-height:1.65;">
                    <strong>⚠ Importante:</strong> Es muy importante que indiques exactamente este concepto para que podamos identificar tu pago correctamente.
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- ── Payment confirmation button ────────────────────────────────── -->
        {% if paymentUrl is defined and paymentUrl %}
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:28px 36px 0;">
            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
              <tr>
                <td style="background-color:#f0f7e6;border:1px solid #c8e6a0;border-radius:12px;padding:22px 24px;">
                  <p style="margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#1a2e1c;">¿Ya has realizado la transferencia?</p>
                  <p style="margin:0 0 18px;font-size:13px;color:#4a5e4c;line-height:1.6;">
                    Una vez completado el pago, pulsa el botón para notificarnos. No es necesario iniciar sesión.
                  </p>
                  <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                    <tr>
                      <td align="center" style="border-radius:8px;background-color:#80ba1b;">
                        <a href="{{ paymentUrl }}"
                           target="_blank"
                           style="display:inline-block;padding:14px 32px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:8px;letter-spacing:0.3px;background-color:#80ba1b;">
                          ✓ Pago realizado
                        </a>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>
        {% endif %}

        <!-- ── Footer ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:32px 36px 36px;">
            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
              <tr>
                <td style="border-top:1px solid #e6e0d4;padding-top:22px;text-align:center;">
                  <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;">Citribio — Gestión de pedidos</p>
                  <p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#a09880;line-height:1.6;">
                    Este presupuesto ha sido generado automáticamente. Si tienes alguna duda, contáctanos en
                    <a href="mailto:administracion@citribio.com" style="color:#567f0b;text-decoration:none;">administracion@citribio.com</a>
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

      </table>
      <!-- /email card -->

    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
